OL,3,CViolent protests target Bangladesh
OL,4,Cstate broadcaster's headquarters
OL,6,FViolent clashes have continued between
OL,7,Fstudents and police in Bangladesh,
OL,8,Fwith protestors setting fire to the
OL,9,Fheadquarters of the state broadcaster.
OL,11,FAt least 25 people are now reported to
OL,12,Fhave died since a wave of
OL,13,Fdemonstrations erupted on Monday.
OL,15,FProtestors are demanding an end to a
OL,16,Fquota system that reserves up to 30%
OL,17,Fof government jobs for relatives of
OL,18,Fveterans who fought in Bangladesh's
OL,19,Fwar of independence in 1971.
