OL,3,CViolent protests target Bangladesh
OL,4,Cstate broadcaster's headquarters
OL,6,FOn Thursday, Bangladesh Television's
OL,7,Fheadquarters was attacked by
OL,8,Fprotestors, who set vehicles and the
OL,9,Fbuilding's reception area on fire.
OL,11,FThe attack came as protestors
OL,12,Fattempted to enforce a "complete
OL,13,Fshutdown" of transportation across the
OL,14,Fcountry apart from emergency services.
OL,16,FHundreds of protestors were chased
OL,17,Fthrough the streets of Dhaka's Uttar
OL,18,Fneighbourhood, while police used
OL,19,Fbatons and tear gas to disperse crowds
OL,20,Fin other locations.
