OL,4,Cstate broadcaster's headquarters
OL,6,FDhaka's Metropolitan Police force
OL,7,Freported a number of injuries -
OL,8,Fincluding to its officers - as a
OL,9,Fresult of the demonstrations.
OL,11,FThe violence, which began at Dhaka
OL,12,FUniversity, is in response to a
OL,13,Fdecision from Bangladesh's High Court
OL,14,Flast month, which overturned a ruling
OL,15,Fto halt job quotas in the country's
OL,16,Fgovernment.
OL,18,FBangladesh's Supreme Court has
OL,19,Fsuspended the ruling and said it will
OL,20,Fmake a final decision next month.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
