OL,6,FRegardless, students have decided to
OL,7,Fvoice their disapproval in the form of
OL,8,Fmass protests.
OL,10,FProtestors have argued the quota
OL,11,Fsystem is discriminatory and benefits
OL,12,Fsupporters of Prime Minister Sheikh
OL,13,FHasina, whose Awami League party led
OL,14,Fthe independence movement.
OL,16,FThey instead want it to be replaced
OL,17,Fwith a merit-based system.
