OL,6,FMs Hasina urged protesters in a
OL,7,Ftelevised address on Wednesday to
OL,8,F"wait with patience" for the court
OL,9,Fverdict, saying: "I believe our
OL,10,Fstudents will get justice from the
OL,11,Fapex court. They will not be
OL,12,Fdisappointed."
OL,14,FAlthough job opportunities have
OL,15,Fexpanded in Bangladesh's private
OL,16,Fsector, many people prefer government
OL,17,Fjobs because they are stable and well-
OL,18,Fpaid.
